item.title: DIY Ruscus Garland
item.dc:creator: user
item.description:
Fresh ruscus garland is an excellent long lasting garland with attractive bright green leaves.

This package contains one bunch of italian ruscus, which is enough to:

- Create a loose, minimalist garland on one eight foot table.

OR

- Nestle around candles, on 4 round tables.

To order for additional table lengths, increase the quantity number in the cart.

SKU: N/A Category: Garlands
Garland Details

This package is for a pre-made  garland, which is enough to create one thick, luxe garland on a eight foot table.

  • Garlands stay fresh an average of 4 days, depending on care and handling.
  • They will dry excellently, and look gorgeous dried!

To order for longer lengths, increase the quantity size in the cart

Garland Care
  • If you have the option of a walk in cooler, wine cellar or just a cool garage or basement you’ll be set.
  • Keep the garland in the original box, out of direct sun and heat until the event.
  • Misting with water will keep the garland fresher for longer
